The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET       

      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 10/2/13


Wednesday, October 02, 2013 10:49 AM




Glenn Beck has reached his snapping point...why? 
 Because he has leaked information from John Boehner's office that proves
 both the Left and Right are in cahoots to exempt themselves from Obamacare
 while the American people are forced to accept it.

  It's time to #DefundtheGOP. 

 Also, as usual Chris Matthews talks complete nonsense and seems to be schizophrenic.

  Plus, Louie Gohmert, a man Glenn truly believes in, joins the show and Glenn wants him to run for senate.
